{"tid":1508574,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[勇武要進化，豬咀都要進化]快啲check下你個豬咀究竟擋唔擋到山埃","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T00:40:16.000Z","uid":193131,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee75bcdadc972bcd6a144952bbd57d76e0b513e","tid":1508574,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"呢排係香港坐係屋企、落街買餸都會中催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨手帶住個豬咀都係好合理的事，佢地教的，自然反應黎呀<br />\n問題係過期催淚彈除左有tg果隻晶體之外仲有山埃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我check左唔少報道，甚至原本話過期催淚彈會出山埃果份學術paper，都只係寫cyanide (氰化物)<br />\n有基本化學知識的人應該明，如果係金屬氰化物例如氰化鉀，唔會係氣體<br />\n所以好快就將目標鎖定係氫氰酸 (Hydrogen cyanide)，因為26度以上佢已經係氣體，好可能係傳媒講的山埃毒氣<br />\n<br />\n如果你戴緊的係單罐3200豬咀，大部分人用緊的3311k其實係冇用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢只係隔有機蒸氣，<span style=\"color: red;\">想隔埋酸性氣體就要買3303k</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你戴緊的係雙罐6200 / 6800 / 7502<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有6003 / 60923 / 60928，可以隔到有機蒸氣+酸性氣體</span><br />\n雖然6006 / 60926係所有類型全包，功能好似最好，但同時間亦代表佢更加快因為其他唔關事的氣體而飽和，壽命較短，而家用緊冇所謂，但唔需要特登買佢<br />\n其他number的濾罐，一係隔唔到有機蒸氣，一係就隔唔到酸性氣體，可免則免<br />\n<br />\n至於另一種過期催淚彈會出現的毒氣光氣 (phosgene)，真係冇一隻濾罐講明可以擋到<br />\n因為正常呢隻野只會係化學武器度出現 (ww1德軍用過)，一定要用到氧氣樽果種面具先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：3M有兩份野去講濾罐濾綿的比較<br />\n<a href=\"https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/40744O/3m-respirator-cartridge-and-filter-selection-poster.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmultimedia.3m.com%2Fmws%2Fmedia%2F40744O%2F3m-respirator-cartridge-and-filter-selection-poster.pdf&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=c9a34977\" target=\"_blank\">https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/40744O/3m-respirator-cartridge-and-filter-selection-poster.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://my15.digitalexperience.ibm.com/9044a799-c194-4640-9cdc-9b5096daacf4/US/Datasheets/99999999999991088803-Datasheet-14368033.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy15.digitalexperience.ibm.com%2F9044a799-c194-4640-9cdc-9b5096daacf4%2FUS%2FDatasheets%2F99999999999991088803-Datasheet-14368033.pdf&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=ac04a643\" target=\"_blank\">https://my15.digitalexperience.ibm.com/9044a799-c194-4640-9cdc-9b5096daacf4/US/Datasheets/99999999999991088803-Datasheet-14368033.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，亦係最重要的<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e92428ba1c0a16eabec62abaed3b4037fafd0c0f","tid":1508574,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f00d101e1dd2f705b7b9a9227d26b2468a02c4be","tid":1508574,"uid":212349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554c5029556b0df1e9a95d9cfedd1c941ba78a25","tid":1508574,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"