-08-27T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"2310cb503488281407d1ca7dd3d34f19eb0f4143","tid":1508574,"uid":28763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d716ac123823fec974143abb336daf48c52cd365","tid":1508574,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"242608b34bc4087c5f794623314243d042b830dd","tid":1508574,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"我睇過係冇一款完美擋到山埃，擋山埃要揹個氧氣樽喺身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6474cf3ae11b35933a7062370037e1d6b0ebbc35","tid":1508574,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eb1b9abc6938d51381184c411484e81fe121fa7","tid":1508574,"uid":193131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"242608b34bc4087c5f794623314243d042b830dd","tid":1508574,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"我睇過係冇一款完美擋到山埃，擋山埃要揹個氧氣樽喺身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"我今日再搵到多一份野，佢的用字好準確，入面寫明係hydrogen cyanide HCN<br />\n(約300度左右tg會分解出HCN) <br />\n所以點解一定要用可以隔埋酸性氣體的濾罐<br />\n希望睇到個post的人幫手宣傳，買濾罐一定要買上面講果幾隻<br />\n山埃仲毒過tg呀，我好驚各位會出事"},{"pid":"03fed51f940523a1c499caf9ac27d76fe4685762","tid":1508574,"uid":93488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:40:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}